article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Jordan Lathon had 22 points in Morehead State's 68-49 victory against Tennessee State on Thursday night. Lathon also contributed 10 rebounds for the Eagles (17-5, 8-1 Ohio Valley Conference). Riley Minix scored 20 points and added seven rebounds. Eddie Ricks III had eight points and was 4 of 8 shooting (0 for 3 from 3-point range). Jason Jitoboh led the Tigers (12-10, 5-4) in scoring, finishing with 12 points and three blocks. Denim Dawson added 10 points for Tennessee State. In addition, EJ Bellinger finished with nine points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
